  {
    "speaker": "interviewee",
    "tag": "JA",
    "text": "[SIGHS] Advice, advice-- I would give my boys advice to carry on, to be aware whenever you see things developing where people are going to get hurt, step in, speak up, demand from our governments to be on the watch. And another request I have right now is to have more children so we can propagate and make up some of the 6 million that we have lost during the Second World War.",
